<br />
<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER><IMG SRC="http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/080902/empcorpse.jpg" WIDTH="280" HEIGHT="153" ALT="" BORDER="0"></TD><TD></TD></TR><TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER><IMG SRC="http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/080902/gebroncloak.jpg" WIDTH="404" HEIGHT="236" ALT="" BORDER="0"><BR>Grats Nindail and <A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=108131">Escad</A>!</TD><TD ALIGN="CENTER"><IMG SRC="http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/080902/shieldofmf.jpg" WIDTH="406" HEIGHT="235" ALT="" BORDER="0"><BR>Grats <A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=50385">Mauleaur</A>!</TD></TR></TABLE><br />
<br />
Thanks to all the recent patches, we actually had a loot dropping blood to go through on the way for a change. No screenshots, since people ninja'd it all too quickly, but grats to <A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=43469">Khaleid</A> on a belt, and <A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=76387">Kumaddara</A> on a mace.<br />
<br />
<HR SIZE=1><br />
<br />
With nothing else of note up, we headed back to VT to see what further changes the patch had brought about.<br />
